# Email preview directories — regenerated on every deploy by the
# `npm run previews` step in netlify.toml's build command. The files
# at /email-previews/*, /email-previews-transactional/*, etc. on the
# live site are always fresh from the latest source. Locally, running
# the generators produces output here that should NOT be committed
# (would create noise in PRs without changing what users see). The
# tracked snapshots in the repo are from earlier manual force-adds
# and remain only as a fallback for environments where Netlify's
# build step can't run.
email-previews/
email-previews-pdf-lead/
email-previews-cart-reengage/
email-previews-founder/
email-previews-member-invitation/
email-previews-gift-flow/
email-previews-transactional/
